        Func {
            bindings = <
&kp HOME        &trans          &trans          &trans           &trans                        &bootloader  &trans    &trans        &trans     &kp PSCRN
&kp LEFT_SHIFT  &trans          &msc SCRL_UP    &trans           &trans                        &trans       &mkp MB1  &kp UP_ARROW  &mkp MB2   &trans
&trans          &msc SCRL_LEFT  &msc SCRL_DOWN  &msc SCRL_RIGHT  &kp K_MUTE                    &trans       &kp LEFT  &kp DOWN      &kp RIGHT  &trans
&kp END         &trans          &trans          &trans           &trans      &trans    &trans  &trans                 &trans        &trans     &trans
            >;
